<HEADLINE> Results of Malaysian Junior Open Squash Championships </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LAMPUR, August 17 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results
from Sunday's finals at the Malaysian Junior Open Squash
