<HEADLINE> Myanmar Sentences Four People for High Treason </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, August 17 (Xinhua) -- A Myanmar township special court
has sentenced four people for act of high treason and association
with unlawful organizations, according to official sources today.
</P>
<P>
Myo Aung Thant was sentenced by the Insein court on August 15
to life imprisonment for committing high treason while Cho Aung
Than, Myint Swe and Nge Ma Ma Than were each given a ten-year
prison term.
</P>
<P>
