troops in Northern province of Sri Lanka, according to a Defense
Ministry news release here today.
</P>
<P>
The release said a group of Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam
(LTTE) rebels Saturday morning attacked government troops at
Uyilankulam in Mannar district.
</P>
