<HEADLINE> Italy Develops Environmental Scientific Research </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, August 16 (Xinhua) -- The Italian National Research
Committee will enhance scientific research on environment this
year and spend 21.4 billion liras (about 12.2 million
U.S. dollars) on the studies.
</P>
