stations already have arrangements for cultural development.
</P>
<P>
In the next three years, Shenzhen will finish its central
library, a 40,000-sq.m. building, and a 30,000-sq.m. concert hall
and a TV broadcasting center.
</P>
<P>
According to municipal government officials, a couple of teams
have been sent to Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou, and Dalian to
study those cities' experiences in cultural development. 
