<P>
The 20-year-old Moya, ranked ninth in the world, is seeking his
third career ATP Tour title. He took the titles at Buenos Aires
in 1995 and Umag, Croatia last year.
</P>
<P>
The 25-year-old Bjorkman, ranked 23rd, advanced to his third
final this year. Today's victory will take him to the top 20 in
next week's ATP Tour rankings for the first time in his career.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
